{"tid":2298232,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"最近開始做遊戲開發（VirusArchimedes)","createTime":"2020-11-24T02:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T03:12:38.000Z","uid":286169,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"47d59c968d3963b4f04c33ab2ba619a4f57cc94d","tid":2298232,"uid":286169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"如題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟完全係新手，有好多嘢都學習中。<br />\n為左試下手，整咗一隻game睇睇情況：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nApp Store：<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/virusarchimedes/id1535807108?l=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fvirusarchimedes%2Fid1535807108%3Fl%3Den&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=486f6e62\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/virusarchimedes/id1535807108?l=en</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sxudio.virusarchimedes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.sxudio.virusarchimedes&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=12965621\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sxudio.virusarchimedes</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play (Lite版）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sxudio.VirusArchimedes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.sxudio.VirusArchimedes&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=eaf8f343\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sxudio.VirusArchimedes</a><br />\n<br />\n相信大家睇到數字就冇曬興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以理解，不過我都搞左幾個月，冇理由唔上架。<br />\n<br />\n總之想聽聽大家意見。"},{"pid":"06836ae23ffe83ca5dad857267d26bfe6574729b","tid":2298232,"uid":286169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20